      "raw_text": "The attorneys in the case OF the\nPalouse Lumber company against the\nNorthern Pacific Railway company\nIRE arguing before the jury In the\nUnited States circuit court today.\nThis is the damage case wherein the\nlumber people are suing the Northern\nPacific for $4,000 for the alleged\nburning of their mill near Palouse\non the night of November Is. The\ncase has taken up most of the week\nand will probably require another day\nbefore going to the jury."
    }
